name: autobahn-js
description: Official Docker repository for AutobahnJS on NodeJS for x86-64.
full_description:
Official Docker repository for [AutobahnJS](https://github.com/crossbario/autobahn-js) on NodeJS for x86-64.

**Please see [here](https://github.com/crossbario/crossbar-starter) for how to getting started.**

Images contain AutobahnJS plus an example client connecting to a WAMP router (configurable, by default `localhost:8080`).

The images are built from [here](https://github.com/crossbario/crossbar-docker/). For a complete list of images, please see [here](https://github.com/crossbario/crossbar-docker#autobahn-js).
